# 🪜 STEP 1: defaults/main.yml (🔥 DYNAMIC VARIABLES)

```yaml
plugin_enabled: true

# List of plugins (one or many)
plugins:
  - name: plugin1.zip
    url: https://artifact.repo/plugin1.zip
  - name: plugin2.zip
    url: https://artifact.repo/plugin2.zip

# Pod selection (dynamic)
plugin_target_label: "app=bi-web"

# OR manual pod list (optional override)
plugin_target_pods: []

plugin_path: /opt/mstr/MicroStrategy/WebASPx/plugins
plugin_tmp_dir: /tmp/plugins
```

