# 🪜 STEP 2: tasks/main.yml

```yaml
- include_tasks: plugin_dynamic.yml
  when: plugin_enabled

- include_tasks: plugin_validate.yml
  when: plugin_enabled
```

---

# 🪜 STEP 3: plugin_dynamic.yml (🔥 CORE LOGIC)

---

## 🔹 1. Create temp dir

```yaml
- name: Create plugin temp directory
  file:
    path: "{{ plugin_tmp_dir }}"
    state: directory
```

---

## 🔹 2. Download ALL plugins dynamically

```yaml
- name: Download plugins
  get_url:
    url: "{{ item.url }}"
    dest: "{{ plugin_tmp_dir }}/{{ item.name }}"
  loop: "{{ plugins }}"
```

---

## 🔹 3. Extract plugins

```yaml
- name: Extract plugins
  unarchive:
    src: "{{ plugin_tmp_dir }}/{{ item.name }}"
    dest: "{{ plugin_tmp_dir }}/{{ item.name | replace('.zip','') }}"
    remote_src: yes
  loop: "{{ plugins }}"
```

---

## 🔹 4. Get target pods (dynamic)

```yaml
- name: Get pods by label (if not manually provided)
  shell: >
    oc get pods -n {{ namespace }} -l {{ plugin_target_label }} -o jsonpath='{.items[*].metadata.name}'
  register: pod_list
  when: plugin_target_pods | length == 0
```

---

## 🔹 5. Set final pod list

```yaml
- set_fact:
    final_pods: "{{ plugin_target_pods if plugin_target_pods | length > 0 else pod_list.stdout.split() }}"
```

---

## 🔹 6. Copy plugins to ALL pods

```yaml
- name: Copy plugins to pods
  shell: >
    oc cp {{ plugin_tmp_dir }}/{{ item_plugin.name | replace('.zip','') }}/.
    {{ namespace }}/{{ item_pod }}:{{ plugin_path }}
  loop: "{{ plugins | product(final_pods) | list }}"
  loop_control:
    loop_var: combo
  vars:
    item_plugin: "{{ combo.0 }}"
    item_pod: "{{ combo.1 }}"
```

---

## 🔹 7. Restart pods

```yaml
- name: Restart pods
  shell: >
    oc delete pod -n {{ namespace }} {{ item }}
  loop: "{{ final_pods }}"
```

---

# 🪜 STEP 4: plugin_validate.yml (🔥 VALIDATION)

---

## 🔹 1. Wait for pods

```yaml
- name: Wait for pods to be running
  shell: >
    oc get pods -n {{ namespace }} -l {{ plugin_target_label }} -o jsonpath='{.items[*].status.phase}'
  register: pod_status
  until: "'Running' in pod_status.stdout"
  retries: 20
  delay: 15
```

---

## 🔹 2. Validate plugin files exist

```yaml
- name: Validate plugins in pods
  shell: >
    oc exec -n {{ namespace }} {{ item }} -- ls {{ plugin_path }}
  register: plugin_check
  loop: "{{ final_pods }}"
```

---

## 🔹 3. Fail if missing

```yaml
- name: Validate plugin presence
  fail:
    msg: "Plugin not found in pod {{ item.item }}"
  when: >
    plugins | map(attribute='name') | map('regex_replace','.zip','') | join('|')
    not in item.stdout
  loop: "{{ plugin_check.results }}"
```

---

## 🔹 4. UI Health Check (🔥 BEST PRACTICE)

```yaml
- name: Validate UI
  shell: >
    curl -k https://{{ dns_entry }}/MicroStrategyLibrary/api/health
  register: ui_check
  failed_when: ui_check.rc != 0
```

